Reasoning: The paper discusses the numerical accuracy of different choices of floating-point number systems, which is a topic related to numerical analysis and scientific computing. Therefore, cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also compares different choices of base in the floating-point systems, which is related to computer arithmetic and could fall under cs.MS (Mathematical Software) or cs.SC (Symbolic Computation). Additionally, the simulations of typical floating-point computations could be related to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.SE (Software Engineering).
